    "ideation": "The Wood emoji is personified as an ancient, stoic, and sturdy entity. It shouldn't be 'bouncy' or 'fast.' Instead, it moves with a heavy, creaking deliberation. The eyes represent knots in the wood, starting as deep, earthy umbers and moving very little. The mouth is the heart of the performance: it represents the grain and the rings of the log. As the log 'settles,' the mouth wave becomes a low-frequency, high-amplitude curve that looks like a growth ring. If it feels a 'splinter' or a 'crack,' the mouth becomes a sharp, high-frequency jagged line momentarily before returning to a dense, solid baseline. The color transitions from a dark bark-brown to a warmer heartwood amber.",
